{"lemma":"قَرَصاتُ","slug":"قَرَصاتُ","root":"ق.ر.ص","root_slug":"ق-ر-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ر-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35488","n35491","n35492"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a pinch, a sting, a bite"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from قَرَصَ (qaraṣa, “to pinch, to bite, to sting”)."},"ipa":["/qar.sˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35488","headword_ar":"قَرَصَهُ","root":"qrS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroSN","text_ar":"قَرْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, Mgh, K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pinched him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the two fingers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a person's skin)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his fingers, so as to pain him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took hold of, it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man's flesh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his two fingers, so as to pain him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he twisted round two fingers upon it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a thing; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the extremities of the fingers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"only: (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he scratched him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, with his nails:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pressed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"squeezed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pinched, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, with the fingers, so as to pain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it with the ends of his fingers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, CK: [one of the explanations of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaroSu","text_ar":"القَرْصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the latter being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaboSu","text_ar":"القَبْصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he seized it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so accord. to a MS. copy of the K, [the inf. n. being there rendered by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaboDu","text_ar":"القَبْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; in the place of which I find in the TA,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqrD","text_ar":"القرض"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this I think a mistranscription;])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the two fingers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in some copies of the K, and in the TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to pain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSahu biZuforayohi","text_ar":"قَرَصَهُ بِظُفْرَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pinched"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his skin with his two nails."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, Msb.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a flea)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bit him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) also said of a gnat; (A, TA;) and of a serpent. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, (tropical:)  [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It pinched him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pained him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] said of the cold. (A, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSa","text_ar":"قَرَصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quruwSapN","text_ar":"قُرُوصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"seems to be another inf. n. of the same,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(beverage)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bit the tongue."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) You say also of [the beverage called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabiy*","text_ar":"نَبِيذ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi quruwSapN","text_ar":"فِيهِ قُرُوصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In it is a biting quality, affecting the tongue."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b5-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSahu bilisaAnihi","text_ar":"قَرَصَهُ بِلِسَانِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb,) inf n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroSN","text_ar":"قَرْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hurt him with his tongue, by saying something which gave pain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, * Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tazaAlu taqoruSuniY minoka","text_ar":"لَا تَزَالُ تَقْرُصُنِى مِنْكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAriSapN","text_ar":"قَارِصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hurtful saying proceeding from thee does not cease to hurt me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSahu","text_ar":"قَرَصَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut it in pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, anything, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between two things;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qr~Shu","text_ar":"قرّصهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or the former signifies [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut it in pieces."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) Hence, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uqoruSiyhi","text_ar":"اُقْرُصِيهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlmaA'i","text_ar":"بِالمَاءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, * Msb, * TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAlmA'","text_ar":"بالماء"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~iSiyhi","text_ar":"قَرِّصِيهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, TA,) said in a trad., (S, M, Msb,) respecting the menstrual blood, (S, M,) accord. to different relations: (S, TA:) the latter means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Separate thou its particles"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so I here render"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~iEiyhi","text_ar":"قَطِّعِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, S, TA;) and the former has a similar [but less intensive] meaning: (TA:) or the former means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wash it with the ends of thy fingers;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and remove it with the nail or the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"off"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the ends of the fingers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rub it hard with the ends of the fingers and the nails, and pour upon it water, so as to remove it and the mark of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, in Msb, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ht","text_ar":"حت"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and IAth, * in TA, in the present art.) ―         -b7-  You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSa","text_ar":"قَرَصَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEajiyna","text_ar":"العَجِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroSN","text_ar":"قَرْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qr~Shu","text_ar":"قرّصهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut the dough to spread it out:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A:) or the former, [simply,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he spread out the dough:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSati AlEajiyna","text_ar":"قَرَصَتِ العَجِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, (S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she cut the dough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spread it out and cut it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into pieces, each such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSap","text_ar":"قُرْصَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qur~Sthu","text_ar":"قُرّصتهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoriySN","text_ar":"تَقْرِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she cut it into many pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSap","text_ar":"قُرْصَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroS","text_ar":"قُرْص"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qariSa","text_ar":"قَرِصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSN","text_ar":"قَرَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAma EalaY AlmunaAfarapi waAlgiybapi","text_ar":"دَامَ عَلَى المُنَافَرَةِ وَالغِيبَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He continued in a course of mutual aversion and defamation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Msb","Mgh","K","TA","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n35491","headword_ar":"قَرْصَةٌ","root":"qrS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSahu","text_ar":"قَرَصَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pinch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pinching:"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSaAtN","text_ar":"قَرَصَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraSahumu","text_ar":"قَرَصَهُمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaEuwDu qaraSaAtK raqaSuwA minohaA raqaSaAtK","text_ar":"البَعُوضُ قَرَصَاتٍ رَقَصُوا مِنْهَا رَقَصَاتٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The gnats bit them with several bitings, in consequence of which they danced with several dancings."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (A, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n35492","headword_ar":"قُرْصَةٌ","root":"qrS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroSN","text_ar":"قُرْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}